[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0495","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0299","title":"FreeBSD lpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 的 lpd（行式打印机守护进程）在处理超长 DNS 主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的打印服务发送特制的主机名数据触发该溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0299"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.117","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至已修复该漏洞的版本（4.0 及以上）。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 lpd 行并重启 inetd 以禁用打印机守护进程；若需继续使用 lpd，在 /etc/hosts.lpd 和白名单中限制允许访问的客户端 IP，并在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 515 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0299","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0299.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/lpd_freebsd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83077/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1283","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1283.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1489","title":"Slackware Linux 3.1 SuperProbe 缓冲区溢出本地提权漏洞","description":"Slackware Linux 3.1 默认安装的 XFree86 SuperProbe 可执行程序默认设置了 setuid root 权限，其 TestChip() 函数在处理长参数时存在 strcpy 缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 -nopr 参数传递超长字符串触发栈溢出，覆盖关键寄存器并执行任意 shellcode，从而完全控制系统并获取 root 用户权限。攻击条件为：本地账户访问权限且 SuperProbe 设置了 setuid root 位。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1489"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-03-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.060","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 到 7.0 或更高版本以获取修复版 XFree86 SuperProbe，并且立即通过执行 chmod u-s /usr/X11/bin/SuperProbe 移除其 setuid 权限。作为临时缓解措施，可以进一步限制普通用户的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19283","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1489.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1489.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19283"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1283.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1344","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1344.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1128","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer .isp 文件远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 3.01 在 Windows 95 系统上存在远程代码执行漏洞。攻击者可构造恶意的 .isp 文件并托管于攻击者控制的网站上，当用户访问该网站时，Internet Explorer 会自动下载并执行该 .isp 文件，且整个过程不会向用户弹出任何安全提示或确认对话框，从而导致未经授权的任意命令在用户系统上执行。该漏洞影响运行 Windows 95 且使用 Internet Explorer 3.01 的用户，攻击条件简单，仅需用户用受影响版本的浏览器访问恶意网站即可触发，无需额外交互或权限提升。由于 IE 3.01 年代久远，官方已不再提供安全更新，建议用户升级至现代浏览器以彻底消除此风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1128"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.813","remediation":"建议立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞在 IE 4.0 中已修复。对于 Windows 95 系统，可安装 Microsoft 后续发布的 IE 安全更新或升级至 Windows 98/2000/XP 等受支持的操作系统。同时配置浏览器安全区域为高等级，禁用自动下载执行 .isp 文件功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://members.tripod.com/~unibyte/iebug3.htm","http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/ie3.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1128.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1128","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1128.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1128.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rvfv-gq5q-pjq9/GHSA-rvfv-gq5q-pjq9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88074/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1128.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e39e743-6138-4277-b505-6305dd52ee05.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1344.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0892","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0612","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 Finger 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"Finger 服务是早期 Unix/Linux 系统中用于查询远程用户信息的网络协议服务（TCP 79 端口）。Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中若开启并运行了 Finger 服务，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过 Finger 协议向目标服务器发送查询请求，获取系统上有效的用户账号列表、用户状态及系统信息等敏感数据。该漏洞无需任何身份验证即可触发，攻击者可利用泄露的用户名信息进行后续暴力破解、社会工程学或定向攻击，从而进一步危害系统安全。受影响范围包括启用了 Finger 服务的 Windows NT 4.0、Windows 2000 Professional/Server 等版本。建议用户关闭系统中不必要的 Finger 服务，禁用 TCP 79 端口监听，以消除信息泄露风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0612"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.177","remediation":"在 Windows NT 4.0 或 Windows 2000 系统中，打开服务管理器找到 Finger 服务，将启动类型设置为「已禁用」并停止该服务。同时，在防火墙中关闭 TCP 79 端口的入站连接，或在注册表中删除或禁用 Finger 服务相关项，以防止未经授权的远程用户查询系统账户信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0612","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/finger/CVE-1999-0612.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2853180ecaf9d7461fd6bb98e4528ce223cae51d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0612.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/324.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/finger.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935/GHSA-8873-vgfq-r935.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0612.md","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/a2a5b448b1c767ec22251b9684e1b2ff2bab4cde/sara/PLIST"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0892.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0530","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0318","title":"HP-UX XMCD 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xmcd 2.0p12 在处理环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响程序传递特制的环境变量参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区边界溢出并覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取目标系统的额外访问权限或提升至更高权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上运行的 xmcd 2.0p12 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级到不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0318"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.507","remediation":"升级 xmcd 至 2.1 及以上版本（该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法升级，可移除 xmcd 二进制文件的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xmcd`；若业务不需要 CD 播放功能，建议直接卸载 xmcd 软件包以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0530.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0241","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0106","title":"多种厂商 Finger 服务手指炸弹漏洞","description":"Finger 服务存在重定向功能滥用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用多个支持 Finger 协议的主机构建重定向链（finger bomb），迫使目标系统反复进行网络连接，造成流量放大或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响早期运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议禁用 Finger 服务或通过防火墙限制入站访问。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0106"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.040","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（如 in.fingerd），在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释掉 finger 行并重启服务。在防火墙上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 79 的访问。如确需使用，通过 tcp_wrappers（/etc/hosts.deny）限制仅允许可信来源 IP。建议升级到支持 finger 访问控制的实现或直接停用该协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0106"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0336","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0165","title":"Linux Linux 内核 NFS 缓存中毒漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）缓存投毒漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标系统上的 NFS 服务发送特制的 RPC 请求来污染客户端缓存，从而将文件操作重定向至恶意服务器，导致敏感信息泄露、文件篡改乃至任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 SunOS、Solaris 及早期 Linux 发行版中运行的 NFS 服务，CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁加以修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0165"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"1997-03-01","remediation":"在 /etc/exports 中使用完全限定域名（FQDN）替代非限定主机名，避免网组（netgroup）配置歧义。同时建议在服务端升级对应厂商补丁（如 Sun、Red Hat、SUSE 等当时的 NFS 安全更新），并在边界防火墙限制外部对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP、2049/UDP）的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0336.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0238","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0105","title":"多款Unix系统 finger 递归查询信息泄露漏洞","description":"finger 服务在处理包含连续 @ 符号的递归查询请求时存在设计缺陷。远程攻击者可通过向目标主机的 finger 服务（默认端口 79）发送精心构造的包含多个 @ 符号的长字符串，触发递归查询机制，导致服务资源被过度消耗从而引发拒绝服务，同时也可被用于跨网络用户信息枚举，泄露系统用户名等敏感信息。该漏洞影响大量运行 finger 服务的 UNIX/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0105"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1997-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.913","remediation":"建议直接禁用 finger 服务（在 inetd 配置中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd 服务），或在网络防火墙层面阻止 TCP 79 端口的入站与出站流量。若业务必须使用，应升级至支持限制递归查询的 fingerd 实现，或限制可查询的用户列表。现代生产环境建议彻底移除 finger 协议及相关软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0105","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0105"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0238.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0868","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris ucbmail 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ucbmail 邮件处理程序存在命令注入漏洞，当从 INN（InterNetNews）新闻传输系统接收邮件时，未能正确过滤邮件内容中的 shell 元字符，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的包含 shell 元字符的邮件数据包触发该漏洞，导致在目标服务器上以邮件服务进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 ucbmail 的 SPARC 架构系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0868"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.473","remediation":"升级 INN 至 1.5.1 版本，并应用 ISC 提供的安全补丁 security-patch.04（下载地址 ftp://ftp.isc.org/isc/inn/patches/security-patch.04）。升级后务必执行 `make update` 并重启 INN 服务。如无法立即升级，可先应用对应版本的补丁（1.5 用 security-patch.01，1.4sec 用 security-patch.02，1.4unoff3/4 用 security-patch.03），再叠加 security-patch.04。同时检查 ucbmail 配置，确保 shell 元字符被正确过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cs.ait.ac.th/joomla3/index.php/security-advisories?CERT/CA97/msg00027.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0868.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0868","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0868.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0868.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5qf7-f7rh-w2xw/GHSA-5qf7-f7rh-w2xw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0868.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b7fcd446-a7f3-414a-8627-a79e05d4c838.json","https://github.com/JackRobert94464/RL-Honeypot/blob/f3b5fce36c605cae51854ec9770537fdb7114f05/Development/TPG-Data/htpg_mini.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1211.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0041","title":"多款Unix系统libc NLS组件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NLS（自然语言服务）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向受影响系统发送特制的 NLS 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 UNICOS 9、MAX 1.3、AIX 4.2、IRIX 6、RedHat 4、Slackware 3、libc 5.2.18 及 mk 1.5 等多个 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。由于涉及系统核心库组件，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0041"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.153","remediation":"对于 Red Hat Linux 4/Slackware 3 等 Linux 系统，应升级至现代发行版并确保 glibc 版本高于 2.0（含 NLS 缓冲区溢出修复）；IBM AIX 4.2 用户请安装 APAR IX70456 补丁或升级至 AIX 5.3 及以上版本；SGI IRIX 6 用户应安装补丁 3369 或升级至 IRIX 6.5.4+。如无法升级，可移除 nls 可执行文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/nls），并限制仅受信用户可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19551","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0041","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0041.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6/GHSA-pqw7-9pjx-g2x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0041.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0250","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0109","title":"Sun Solaris ffbconfig 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 的 ffbconfig 图形配置工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 ffbconfig 程序传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统账号才能利用此漏洞实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0109"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.407","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #140 提供的补丁程序，或直接升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/sbin/ffbconfig 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ffbconfig），限制本地非授权用户执行该命令，防止普通用户利用缓冲区溢出提权至 root。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b1