PC 请求时的拒绝服务问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持且不再接收安全更新，建议升级至仍在支持周期内的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：在不需要 RPC Locator 服务的环境中，通过 services.msc 将 Remote Procedure Call (RPC) Locator 服务启动类型设为\"禁用\"，或在防火墙上限制对该服务端口 (TCP 135) 的不必要访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ162567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0228","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0228.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0046","title":"多款Unix系统 rlogin TERM环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rlogin 程序在处理 TERM 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、Digital UNIX、FreeBSD、HP-UX、IBM AIX、NetBSD、NeXTstep、SGI IRIX、SunOS 等多种 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0046"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.963","remediation":"针对各受影响系统版本，建议立即升级至修复版本（如 FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、HP-UX 11.00 及以上、IBM AIX 4.2 及以上）；如无法升级，可移除 rlogin 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/rlogin）或禁用 rlogin 服务（注释 inetd.conf 中 login 行并重启 inetd），改用 SSH 替代 rlogin 进行远程登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0046","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19203","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0046","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0046.json","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0046.md","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/622953dc0146a9a48737afdaeb97da06c1b9895d/1999/CVE-1999-0046.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0116.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0494","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0298","title":"SunOS ypbind 路径遍历文件覆盖漏洞","description":"SunOS 与 Linux Slackware 系统中 ypbind 服务在启用 -ypset 或 -ypsetme 选项时存在路径遍历漏洞。远程或本地攻击者可通过构造包含 ..（点点）的特殊请求，绕过目录限制覆盖系统任意文件，导致权限提升或服务异常。该漏洞影响运行 ypbind 且开启上述选项的 SunOS 及 Slackware 系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0298"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.990","remediation":"禁止使用 -ypset 和 -ypsetme 参数启动 ypbind，仅允许通过 ypserv 配置文件（/var/yp/securenets）确定的受信 NIS 服务器绑定。在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 111 和 32770-32800 的外部访问，或禁用 NIS 改用 LDAP 认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/06_ypbindsetme_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0298","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1441/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000146.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1463","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1463.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1299","title":"Linux rcp 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Linux 系统 rcp 命令存在文件权限处理漏洞。当用户 UID 为 65535（即 nobody 用户）时，系统调用 chown 将该值解释为 -1 导致文件所有权修改失败，从而使低权限的 nobody 用户能够覆写任意系统文件。攻击者只需获取 nobody 账户权限即可利用此漏洞，影响 Red Hat 4.0 等早期 Linux 发行版，可导致系统文件被恶意篡改，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1299"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-02-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.643","remediation":"立即停止使用 rcp 命令，改用 scp 或 rsync 替代。将系统升级至 Red Hat 5.0 及以上版本，修复 UID 65535 被错误解析为 -1 的内核缺陷。如无法升级，移除 rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod -s /usr/bin/rcp，并限制可执行 rcp 的用户组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420509&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1299.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1299","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1299.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1299.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h2pr-xxm8-wv36/GHSA-h2pr-xxm8-wv36.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0